id: pm-cfed
title: "GH-435: lean JSON output mode omitting null/empty fields (~50% token cut for --json)"
description: "Dogfood GH-435: --json is ~50% larger than TOON because it serializes all-null filters echoes and empty containers; add a lean JSON mode. Duplicate check: searched lean json/omit null/compact output — only MCP compact defaults (closed 2026-05-20) and mutation compactness (GH-437 item) matched; no open overlap."
